      <title>谷歌应该对 Facebook 采取 Android 策略</title>
      <link>https://linguage.github.io/naval/zh/google-should-pull-an-android-on-facebook.zh/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Jul 2011 04:23:18 +0000</pubDate>
